OL,3,CCourt recommends 17.75% pay rise for
OL,4,CAer Lingus pilots
OL,6,FAer Lingus should increase pilots' pay
OL,7,Fby 17.75%, according to
OL,8,Frecommendations by the Irish Labour
OL,9,FCourt.
OL,11,FIt comes amid a high-profile
OL,12,Findustrial relations dispute which has
OL,13,Fresulted in hundreds of flight
OL,14,Fcancellations.
OL,16,FThe proposal follows meetings at the
OL,17,FLabour Court involving representatives
OL,18,Ffrom Aer Lingus and the Irish Air Line
OL,19,FPilots' Association (Ialpa).
