OL,3,CCourt recommends 17.75% pay rise for
OL,4,CAer Lingus pilots
OL,6,FIf implemented, the pay deal would
OL,7,Fcover a four-year period from January
OL,8,F1 2023 to the end of 2026.
OL,10,FIalpa officers and representatives
OL,11,Ffrom the Forsa trade union are
OL,12,Fconsidering the non-binding
OL,13,Frecommendations.
OL,15,FThe pilots had initially been seeking
OL,16,Fa pay increase of 24%, which they say
OL,17,Fequates to inflation since the last
OL,18,Fpay rise in 2019.
