OL,3,CCourt recommends 17.75% pay rise for
OL,4,CAer Lingus pilots
OL,6,FHowever, Ialpa later said that it
OL,7,Fwould be willing to consider a lower
OL,8,Fpay increase.
OL,10,FBut it accused Aer Lingus of not
OL,11,Fmaking a similar compromise to move
OL,12,Ffrom its offer of 12.25%, without
OL,13,Frequests for pilots to improve
OL,14,Fproductivity.
OL,16,FThe pilots' group also rejected a
OL,17,Fprevious interim Labour Court
OL,18,Frecommendation for pay increases of
OL,19,F9.25% last month.
