OL,3,CCourt recommends 17.75% pay rise for
OL,4,CAer Lingus pilots
OL,6,FAer Lingus has cancelled hundreds of
OL,7,Fflights during the pilots' indefinite
OL,8,Fwork-to-rule, which began at the end
OL,9,Fof June, in an effort to protect
OL,10,Fservices from the "highly disruptive"
OL,11,Findustrial action.
OL,13,FIn a statement on Monday, the airline
OL,14,Fsaid: "Aer Lingus will carefully
OL,15,Freview the final recommendation of the
OL,16,FLabour Court.
OL,18,F"The company will confirm its position
OL,19,Ffollowing completion of that review."
